--:_ACID_GRIP|
--&Spell_Name|Acid Grip
--&Spell_Source|PC1
--&Page|316
--&Spell_Focus|
--&Spell_Level|2
--&Spell_Traits|acid, concentrate, manipulate
--&Spell_Domains|
--&Spell_Subclass|
--&Spell_Traditions|arcane, primal
--&Casting_Time|2 actions
--&Spell_Components|
--&Spell_Trigger|
--&Spell_Requirements|
--&Spell_Range|120 feet
--&Spell_Area_Type|
--&Spell_Area_Description|
--&Spell_Saving_Throw|Reflex
--&Spell_Targets|1 creature
--&Spell_Duration|
--&Spell_Description|An ephemeral, taloned hand grips the target, burning it with magical acid. The target takes 2d8 acid damage plus 1d6 Persistent Acid Damage depending on its Reflex save. A creature taking rsistent damage from this spell takes a –10-foot status bonus to its Speeds.
--&Critical_Success|The creature is unaffected.
--&Success|The creature takes half damage and no persistent damage, and the claw moves it up to 5 feet in a direction of your choice.
--&Failure|The creature takes full damage and persistent damage, and the claw moves it up to 10 feet in a direction of your choice.
--&Critical_Failure|The creature takes double damage and full persistent damage, and the claw moves it up to 20 feet in a direction of your choice.
--&Affliction|
--&Heightened_Effects|Heightened (+2): The initial damage increases by 2d8, and the Persistent Acid Damage increases by 1d6.
--&Amp|
--^_SPELL_PRINT|

--:_ACID_SPLASH|
--&Spell_Name|Acid Splash
--&Spell_Source|CRB
--&Page|316
--&Spell_Focus|
--&Spell_Level|1
--&Spell_Traits|acid, attack, cantrip, evocation
--&Spell_Domains|
--&Spell_Subclass|
--&Spell_Traditions|arcane, primal
--&Casting_Time|2 actions
--&Spell_Components|Somatic, Verbal
--&Spell_Trigger|
--&Spell_Requirements|
--&Spell_Range|30 feet
--&Spell_Area_Type|
--&Spell_Area_Description|
--&Spell_Saving_Throw|
--&Spell_Targets|1 creature
--&Spell_Duration|
--&Spell_Description|You splash a glob of acid that splatters your target and nearby creatures. Make a spell attack. If you hit, you deal 1d6 acid damage plus 1 splash acid damage. On a critical success, the target so takes 1 Persistent Acid Damage.
--&Critical_Success|
--&Success|
--&Failure|
--&Critical_Failure|
--&Affliction|
--&Heightened_Effects|Heightened 3: The initial damage increases to 1d6 + your spellcasting ability modifier, and the Persistent Damage increases to 2.
[br]Heightened 5: The initial damage increases to 2d6 + your spellcasting ability modifier, the Persistent Damage increases to 3, and the splash damage increases to 2.
[br]Heightened 7: The initial damage increases to 3d6 + your spellcasting ability modifier, the Persistent Damage increases to 4, and the splash damage increases to 3.
[br]Heightened 9: The initial damage increases to 4d6 + your spellcasting ability modifier, the Persistent Damage increases to 5, and the splash damage increases to 4.
--&Amp|
--^_SPELL_PRINT|

