[br]●[b]Pterosaur[/b] Speed 10 feet, fly Speed 40 feet; imprecise scent 30 feet
[br][b]Melee[/b] [&One_Action] beak, [b]Damage[/b] 3d6 piercing.
[br]●[b]Wasp[/b] Speed 20 feet, fly Speed 40 feet
