You can Dismiss the spell.
You gain the following statistics and abilities regardless of the form that you choose:
[br]●AC = 20 + your level. Ignore your armor check's penalty and Speed reduction.
[br]●30 temporary Hit Points, weakness 5 to cold iron, and weakness 5 to good. Darkvision.
[br]●One or more attacks specific to the battle form you use. You're trained with them. Your attack modifier is +22, and you use the listed damage. These attacks are Strength based (for the purpose of the Enfeebled condition, for example). If your attack modifier is higher for the given unarmed attack or weapon, you can use it instead.
