[br][f[=[&bodyFontSize]+1]\\][b]Hezrou[/b][/f] Speed 30 feet, swim 30 feet
[br][b]Melee[/b] [&One_Action] jaws (reach (10 feet)), [b]Damage[/b] 2d12+10 piercing plus 1d6 evil, and you can spend an action after a hit to Grab the target
[br][b]Melee[/b] [&One_Action] claw (agile, reach (10 feet)), [b]Damage[/b] 2d8 slashing plus 1d6 evil.
[br][f[=[&bodyFontSize]+1]\\][b]Nabasu[/b][/f] Speed 25 feet, fly 40 feet
[br][b]Melee[/b] [&One_Action] jaws, [b]Damage[/b] 2d10+10 piercing plus 1d6 evil
[br][b]Melee[/b] [&One_Action] claw (agile), [b]Damage[/b] 2d6 slashing plus 1d6 evil.
[br][f[=[&bodyFontSize]+1]\\][b]Vrock[/b][/f] Speed 25 feet, fly 35 feet; resistance 10 to electricity
[br][b]Melee[/b] [&One_Action] beak, [b]Damage[/b] 2d8+10 piercing plus 1d6 evil
[br][b]Melee[/b] [&One_Action] claw (agile), [b]Damage[/b] 2d6 slashing plus 1d6 evil
