[br][f[=[&bodyFontSize]+1]\\][b]Osyluth[/b][/f] Speed 35 feet, fly 30 feet
[br][b]Melee[/b] [&One_Action] jaws, [b]Damage[/b] 2d10+10 piercing plus 1d6 evil
[br][b]Melee[/b] [&One_Action] claw (agile, reach (10 feet)), [b]Damage[/b] 2d6 slashing plus 1d6 evil
