If you were Medium or smaller, you become Large, as the effects of enlarge. You must have space to expand into, or the spell is lost. You also gain the following benefits.
[br]●40 temporary Hit Points.
[br]●A fly Speed equal to your Speed.
[br]●Weakness 10 to the alignment opposite the one you chose.
[br]●A +1 status bonus to saves against spells.
[br]●Darkvision.
[br]●Your unarmed attacks and weapons deal 1 additional damage of the chosen alignment type.
[br]●One or more unarmed melee attacks. If you chose good or lawful, your fist attacks deal 2d8 damage. If you chose chaotic, you gain a bite unarmed attack that deals 2d10 piercing damage. If you chose evil, you gain a claws unarmed attack that deals 2d8 slashing damage and has the agile and finesse traits.
