--&Spell_Description_O|Calling upon powerful transformative magic, you gain a Large dragon battle form. you must have space to expand or the spell is lost. when you cast this spell, choose one type of chromatic or metallic dragon. while in this form, you gain the dragon trait.
You have hands in this battle form and can take manipulate actions. You can dismiss the spell.
You gain the following statistics and abilities regardless of which battle form you choose:
[br]●AC = 18 + your level. Ignore your armor's check penalty and Speed reduction.
[br]●10 temporary Hit Points
[br]●Speed 40 feet, fly Speed 100 feet 
[br]●Resistance 10 against the damage type of your breath weapon (see below)
