--&Failure|[?"X[&Remastered]" -ne "X"||The creature takes the full collapse damage and falls Prone.]
--&Critical_Failure|[?"X[&Remastered]" -ne "X"||The creature takes the full collapse damage and falls into a fissure.]
--&Affliction|
--&Heightened_Effects|Heightened 10: You create a massive earthquake that can devastate a settlement. The range increases to half a mile and the area to a quarter-mile burst.
