[br]●[b]Water[/b] The target takes on a watery sheen, gaining resistance 5 to fire and a swim Speed equal to its land Speed.
[br]●[b]Wood[/b] The target gains a number of temporary Hit Points equal to the spell's rank, then gains half that number of temporary HP at the start of each of its turns.
