[br]Size Small
[br][b]Melee[/b] [&One_Action] scythe (deadly (d10), trip), [b]Damage[/b] 1d10+8 slashing
[br][b]Melee[/b] [&One_Action] boot (agile, versatile (B)), [b]Damage[/b] 1d6 piercing. 
[br][f[=[&bodyFontSize]+1]\\][b]Unicorn[/b] gain the beast trait in addition to fey; Speed 40 feet; resistance 5 to poison; Size Large
