[br][&Two_Action] (concentrate) The spell has a range of 30 feet. If you're healing a living creature, increase the Hit Points restored by 8.
[br][&Three_Action] (concentrate) You disperse vital energy in a 30-foot emanation. This targets all living and undead creatures in the burst.
