[br][&One_Action] (somatic) The spell has a range of touch.
[br][&Two_Action] (verbal, somatic) The spell has a range of 30 feet. If you're healing a living creature, increase the Hit Points restored by 8.
[br][&Three_Action] (material, somatic, verbal) You disperse positive energy in a 30-foot emanation. This targets all living and undead creatures in the burst.]
