--&Success|The creature is unaffected.
--&Failure|Within the next hour, the creature must roll its next two attack rolls twice and take the lower result.
--&Critical_Failure|Within the next hour, the creature must roll its next four attack rolls twice and take the lower result.
--&Affliction|
--&Heightened_Effects|
--&Amp|
