[br]●[b]Mountain[/b] The target isn't Flat-Footed when climbing, and when it rolls a success on an acrobatics check to balance on rubble, it gets a critical success instead.
[br]●[b]Plains[/b] The target gains a +10-foot status bonus to its land speed.
[br]●[b]Underground[/b] The target gains darkvision.
