[br]●[b]Reduce a Condition[/b] Reduce the value of the target's Clumsy, Enfeebled, or Stupefied condition by 2. You can instead reduce two of the listed conditions by 1 each.
[br][b]Lessen a Toxin[/b] Reduce the stage of one toxin the target suffers from by one stage. This can't reduce the stage below stage 1 or cure the affliction.
