--&Casting_Time|1 action
--&Spell_Components|Somatic
--&Spell_Trigger|
--&Spell_Requirements|
--&Spell_Range|60 feet
--&Spell_Area_Type|
--&Spell_Area_Description|
--&Spell_Saving_Throw|
--&Spell_Targets|you and 1 ally
