--&Casting_Time|3 actions
--&Spell_Components|Material, Somatic, Verbal
--&Spell_Trigger|
--&Spell_Requirements|You have a deity.
--&Spell_Range|100 feet
--&Spell_Area_Type|
--&Spell_Area_Description|
--&Spell_Saving_Throw|
--&Spell_Targets|
--&Spell_Duration|until the end of your next turn
--&Spell_Description|
[b]Lawful Good: Arrive[/b] (Enchantment, Good, Lawful) [i]Aura Of Retribution[/i] While within 100 feet of the herald, you and your allies gain the champion's Retributive Strike reaction
[br][b]Depart[/b] [i]Holy Smite[/i] The herald casts 5th-level Divine Wrath (choosing good) in a 100-foot emanation.
[br][b]Neutral Good: Arrive[/b] (Enchantment, Good) [i]Aura Of Redemption[/i] While within 100 feet of the herald, you and your allies gain the champion's Glimpse of Redemption reaction
[br][b]Depart[/b] [i]Merciful Healing[/i] The herald casts the 3-action version of 5th-level Heal with a radius of 100 feet. This spell targets only you and your allies.
[br][b]Chaotic Good: Arrive[/b] (Chaotic, Enchantment, Good) [i]Aura Of Liberation[/i] While within 100 feet of the herald, you and your allies gain the champion's Liberating Step reaction
[br][b]Depart[/b] [i]Radiating Freedom[/i] The herald affects you and all your allies within 100 feet with Freedom Of Movement. The duration is reduced to 3 rounds.
[br][b]Lawful Neutral: Arrive[/b] (Abjuration, Lawful) [i]Defy Chaos[/i] You and each ally within 100 feet of the herald gain resistance 20 against chaotic damage while the herald is present
[br][b]Depart[/b] [i]Order's Wrath[/i] The herald casts 5th-level Divine Wrath (choosing lawful) in a 100-foot emanation.
[br][b]Neutral: Arrive[/b] (Transmutation) [i]Quickening Ripple[/i] You and each ally within 100 feet of the herald are Quickened while the herald is present, and can use the additional action to Step, Stride, or Strike
[br][b]Depart[/b] [i]Sapping Beam[/i] The herald casts 6th-level Enervation in a 100-foot line.
[br][b]Chaotic Neutral: Arrive[/b] (Abjuration, Chaotic) [i]Defy Law[/i] You and each ally within 100 feet of the herald gain resistance 20 against lawful damage while the herald is present
[br][b]Depart[/b] [i]Chaos Hammer[/i] The herald casts 5th-level Divine Wrath (choosing chaotic) in a 100-foot emanation.
[br][b]Lawful Evil: Arrive[/b] [i]Aura Of Iron[/i] While within 100 feet of the herald, you and your allies gain the champion's Iron Command reaction
[br][b]Depart[/b] [i]Unholy Blight[/i] The herald casts 5th-level Divine Wrath (choosing evil) in a 100-foot emanation.
[br][b]Neutral Evil: Arrive[/b] [i]Aura Of Selfishness[/i] While within 100 feet of the herald, you and your allies gain the champion's Selfish Shield reaction
[br][b]Depart[/b] [i]Infinite Despair[/i] The herald casts 5th-level Crushing Despair in a 100-foot cone.
[br][b]Chaotic Evil: Arrive[/b] [i]Aura Of Vengeance[/i] While within 100 feet of the herald, you and your allies gain the champion's Destructive Vengeance reaction
[br][b]Depart[/b] [i]Weapon Hurricane[/i] The herald casts 5th-level Weapon Storm in a 100-foot cone, using d12 for the die size.
