--&Spell_Description|"[b]Agmazar The Star Titan[/b] Speed 100 feet, climb 50 feet
[br][b]Arrive[/b] (Necromancy, Negative) [i]Channel Void[/i] Each foe in a 100-foot emanation takes 16d8 negative energy damage with a basic Fortitude save
[br][b]Depart[/b] (Transmutation) Gravitic Repulsion Each foe in a 50-foot emanation is pushed 100 feet away unless it succeeds at a Fortitude save.
[br][b]Agyra, The Forever Storm[/b] Speed 80 feet, fly 200 feet
[br][b]Arrive[/b] (Electricity, Evocation) [i]Breath of a Thousand Storms[/i] Agyra shoots two 1,200-foot lines of electricity, one from each of her heads. The lines can't overlap. Each creature along one of the lines takes 6d12 electricity damage with a basic Reflex save. On a failure, the creature is also Slowed 1 for 1 round (or for 1 minute on a critical failure)
[br][b]Depart[/b] (Evocation, Sonic) [i]Thunderous Blast[/i] Each creature within a 100-foot emanation takes 6d10 sonic damage with a basic Reflex save, and is also knocked Prone on a failed save.
[br][b]Bezravnis, The Inferno Below[/b] Speed 100 feet, burrow 100 feet
[br][b]Arrive[/b] (Earth, Evocation) [i]Burrow from the Earth's Heart[/i] Bezravnis explodes from the ground where it was summoned, causing all creatures in a 50-foot emanation to take 8d12 bludgeoning damage with a basic Reflex save. This potentially collapses structures with the collapse effect of the Earthquake spell, except there is no chance of falling into a fissure
[br][b]Depart[/b] [i]Web Hurricane[/i] Bezravnis departs with a hurricane of webbing. All creatures within a 50-foot emanation must succeed at a Reflex save or take a \u201320-foot circumstance penalty to its Speeds until it Escapes (or is Immobilized until it escapes on a critical failure). The Escape DC is your Spell DC.
[br][b]Mogaru, The Final King[/b] Speed 100 feet, swim 100 feet
[br][b]Arrive[/b] (Auditory, Enchantment, Mental) [i]Trance of the King's Melody[/i] Mogaru manifests with a burst of the song that summoned him, requiring all foes within 60 feet who can hear him to attempt a Will save, leaving them Stunned 3 on a failure
[br][b]Depart[/b] (Evocation, Fire) [i]Volcanic Breath[/i] Mogaru unleashes his scorching breath in a 120-foot cone. Each creature in the area takes 10d6 fire damage with a basic Reflex save. On a failure, it also takes 4d6 Persistent Fire Damage.
[br][b]Vorgozen, The Shapeless Feeder[/b] Speed 50 feet, climb 50 feet, swim 100 feet
[br][b]Arrive[/b] (Necromancy) [i]Pollute Magic[/i] Vorgozen's foul presence pollutes magic around her. Each of your enemies within a 60-foot emanation that are under the effects of a spell must attempt a Fortitude save. On a failure, the creature is Sickened 2. Any of your enemies that Casts a Spell within 60 feet of Vorgozen must attempt a Fortitude save with the same effects unless it's already Sickened
[br][b]Depart[/b] (Acid, Evocation) [i]Beam of Purest Vitriol[/i] Each creature in a 1,200-foot line takes 10d6 acid damage and 10d6 bludgeoning damage with a basic Fortitude save.
[br][b]Yarthoon, The Moon Grub[/b] Speed 60 feet, burrow 100 feet, fly 100 feet, swim 100 feet
[br][b]Arrive[/b] (Cold, Evocation) [i]Algid Beam Barrage[/i] Yarthoon fires countless beams, targeting each of your enemies within 200 feet of it. The beams deal 10d6 cold damage with a basic Reflex save
[br][b]Depart[/b] (Cold, Conjuration, Water) [i]Frostbite Mist[/i] Chilling mist surges out in a 100-foot burst centered on Yarthoon and remains for 1 minute. This mist has the effects of Obscuring Mist, plus any creature within the area at the end of its turn take 5d6 cold damage with a basic Fortitude save.
[br][b]Ebeshra, The Winged Razor[/b] Speed 75 feet, fly 100 feet
[br][b]Arrive[/b] (Conjuration, Teleportation) [i]Planar Draw[/i] Each foe in a 100-foot emanation is pulled 50 feet towards the center, unless it succeeds at a Fortitude save. Creatures that fail and reach the center take 10d6 bludgeoning damage
[br][b]Depart[/b] (Electricity, Evocation) [i]Storm Discharge[/i] Each foe in a 240-foot line takes 12d8 electricity damage with a basic Reflex save"
