[br]Heightened 4: The creature can be level 3 or lower.|Heightened 2: Level 1.
[br]Heightened 3: Level 2. You can summon a Black Bear, giant bat, or leopard.
[br]Heightened 4: Level 3. You can summon a great white shark or tiger.]
