[br]Heightened 9: You and the other targets can travel to any location on another planet within the same solar system. Assuming you have accurate knowledge of the location's position and appearance, you arrive on the new planet 100 miles off target.
[br]Heightened 10: As the 9th-level version, but you and the other targets can travel to any planet within the same galaxy.
--&Amp|
