[br]Heightened 9: The turtle's size increases to Gargantuan, making it capable of carrying two Huge creatures, up to eight Large creatures, up to 32 Medium creatures, or up to 64 Small creatures. Its swim Speed increases to 60 feet, and the duration increases to 1 month.
