[br]●If you have Insect Shape, you can instead transform your mouth into wild jaws, an unarmed attack you're trained in that deals 1d8 piercing damage.
[br]●If you have Elemental Shape, you can morph your body to be partially composed of elemental matter, granting you resistance 5 to critical hits and precision damage. 
[br]●If you have Plant Shape, you can morph your arms into long vines, increasing your reach to 10 feet (or 15 feet with a reach weapon).
[br]●If you have Soaring Shape, you can cast the spell as a two-action activity (somatic, verbal) to grow wings from your back. These wings allow you to Fly with a fly Speed of 30 feet.
